a to operate two Bodrum charters in summer 2020|url=https://centreforaviation.com/news/air-astana-to-operate-two-bodrum-charters-in-summer-2020-977012|accessdate=19 February 2020 |work=CAPA |date=19 February 2020}}</ref> [[Kittil\u00e4 Airport|Kittila]]|<ref>{{cite web|title=Online timetable |website=Air Astana|url=https://airastana.com/global/en-us/Plan/Flight-Information/Timetable|accessdate=November 25, 2019}}</ref>\n<!-- -->\n| [[Air Astana]]<br />{{nowrap|operated by [[FlyArystan]]}} |[[Aktobe Airport|Aktobe]], [[Almaty International Airport|Almaty]], [[Kostanay Airport|Kostanay]], [[Kyzylorda Airport|Kyzylorda]], [[Zhukovsky International Airport|Moscow\u2013Zhukovsky]], [[Pavlodar Airport|Pavlodar]], [[Petropavl Airport|Petropavl]], [[Semey Airport|Semey]], [[Shymkent Airport|Shymkent]], [[Taraz Airport|Taraz]] |<ref>{{cite web|title=Online Timetable |website=FlyArystan|url=https://booking.flyarystan.com/web/FlightSchedule.xhtml|accessdate=November 25, 2019}}</ref>\n<!-- -->\n| [[Air China]] | [[Beijing Capital International Airport|Beijing\u2013Capital]] |<ref>{{cite web|title=Online timetable |website=Air China|url=http://www.airchina.com.cn/en/service/flight-time-search/flight-time.shtml|accessdate=August 5, 2018}}</ref>\n<!-- -->\n| [[Bek Air]] | [[Aktau Airport|Aktau]], [[Aktobe Airport|Aktobe]], [[Almaty International Airport|Almaty]], [[Atyrau Airport|Atyrau]], [[Kyzylorda Airport|Kyzylorda]], [[Oral Ak Zhol Airport|Oral]], [[Oskemen Airport|Oskemen]], [[Shymkent Airport|Shymkent]] |<ref>{{cite web|title=Online Timetable |website=Bek Air|url=https://www.bekair.aero/en/flights/timetable/|accessdate=November 25, 2019}}</ref>\n<!-- -->\n| [[Belavia]] | [[Minsk National Airport|Minsk]]  |<ref>{{cite web|title=Online Timetable\n|website=Belavia|url=https://en.belavia.by/time-table/|accessdate=November 25, 2019}}</ref>\n<!-- -->\n| {{nowrap| [[China Southern Airlines]]}} | [[Guangzhou Baiyun International Airport|Guangzhou]]{{ref|a|a}}, [[\u00dcr\u00fcmqi Di