 Airways Announces Eight New Destinations at the Kuwait Aviation Show 2020 |url=https://www.qatarairways.com/en/press-releases/2020/January/KAS2020.html?activeTag=Press-releases |publisher=Qatar Airways |accessdate=16 January 2020}}</ref>\n<!-- -->\n| [[Qazaq Air]] | [[Aktobe Airport|Aktobe]], [[Almaty Airport|Almaty]],  [[Kostanay Airport|Kostanay]], [[Oskemen Airport|Oskemen]],  [[Petropavl Airport|Petropavl]],  [[Shymkent Airport|Shymkent]], [[Taldykorgan Airport|Taldykorgan]], [[Zhezkazgan Airport|Zhezkazgan]] |<ref>{{cite web|title=Online Timetable|website=Qazaq Air|url=https://www.flyqazaq.com/en/flights-schedule?airportCode=TSE|accessdate=November 25, 2019}}</ref>\n<!-- -->\n| [[S7 Airlines]] | [[Moscow Domodedovo Airport|Moscow\u2013Domodedovo]] (begins {{date|2020-5-26}}),<ref>{{cite news |last1=Liu |first1=Jim |title=S7 Airlines adds Moscow \u2013 Nur-Sultan route from late-May 2020 |url=https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/287881/s7-airlines-adds-moscow-nur-sultan-route-from-late-may-2020/ |accessdate=3 December 2019 |work=Routesonline |date=3 December 2019}}</ref> [[Tolmachevo Airport|Novosibirsk]] |<ref>{{cite web|title=Online Timetable |website=S7 Airlines|url=https://www.s7.ru/en/timetable/?departureCity=TSE|accessdate=November 25, 2019}}</ref>\n<!-- -->\n| [[SCAT Airlines]] | [[Aktau Airport|Aktau]], [[Aktobe Airport|Aktobe]], [[Almaty International Airport|Almaty]], [[Atyrau Airport|Atyrau]], [[Dushanbe International Airport|Dushanbe]], [[Mineralnye Vody Airport|Mineralnye Vody]], [[Vnukovo International Airport|Moscow\u2013Vnukovo]], [[Oral Ak Zhol Airport|Oral]], [[Oskemen Airport|Oskemen]], [[Pavlodar Airport|Pavlodar]], [[Prague V\u00e1clav Havel Airport|Prague]], [[Semey Airport|Semey]], [[Shymkent Airport|Shymkent]], [[Taraz Airport|Taraz]], [[Chinggis Khaan International Airport|Ulaanbaatar]], [[Xi'an Xianyang International Airport|Xi'an]], [[Yerevan International Airport|Yerevan]] <br>'''Seasonal:''' [[Batumi International Airpo