oeing 737-800]].<ref>{{cite news|last1=L|first1=J|title=China Southern Airlines to commence Guangzhou-Urumqi-Astana service|url=https://centreforaviation.com/news/china-southern-airlines-to-commence-guangzhou-urumqi-astana-service-887213|publisher=CAPA|date=14 March 2019}}</ref>\n\n===Cargo===\n{{Airport-dest-list\n<!-- -->\n| [[Silk Way Airlines]] | [[Heydar Aliyev International Airport|Baku]], [[Hong Kong International Airport|Hong Kong]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Turkish Airlines Cargo]] | [[Hong Kong International Airport|Hong Kong]], [[Istanbul Atat\u00fcrk Airport|Istanbul\u2013Atat\u00fcrk]]\n<!-- -->\n}}\n\n==Statistics==\n\n===Passenger figures===\n<center>\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Passengers\n! Change on previous year\n!| Nursultan Nazarbayev International Airport Passenger Totals 2004\u20132019\n|-\n| 2004\n| 496,240<ref name=\"kase.kz\">http://www.kase.kz/files/emitters/ARAL/aralp_2016_rus.pdf \u041a\u043e\u043b\u0438\u0447\u0435\u0441\u0442\u0432\u043e \u043e\u0431\u0441\u043b\u0443\u0436\u0435\u043d\u043d\u044b\u0445 \u043f\u0430\u0441\u0441\u0430\u0436\u0438\u0440\u043e\u0432 \u0432 \u0430\u044d\u0440\u043e\u043f\u043e\u0440\u0442\u0430\u0445 \u0420\u0435\u0441\u043f\u0443\u0431\u043b\u0438\u043a\u0438 \u041a\u0430\u0437\u0430\u0445\u0441\u0442\u0430\u043d \u0437\u0430 2015-2016 \u0433\u0433.\u0441\u0442\u0440 39</ref>\n|{{increase}}{{0}}24.9%\n| rowspan=\"20\" style=\"background:#fff;\"| <timeline>\nImageSize = width:auto height:250 barincrement:30\nPlotArea = left:30 bottom:15 top:11 right:15\nAlignBars = justify\nPeriod = from:0 till:5\nTimeAxis = orientation:vertical\n\nColors =\n id:gray value:gray(0.5)\n id:line1 value:gray(0.9)\n id:line2 value:gray(0.7)\n\nScaleMajor = start:3 increment:1 gridcolor:line2\nScaleMinor = start:3 increment:1 gridcolor:line1\n\nPlotData=\n color:blue width:20\n bar:2004 from:start till:0.496\n bar:2005 from:start till:0.658\n bar:2006 from:start till:0.834\n bar:2007 from:start till:1.171\n bar:2008 from:start t